snippet.title: FATE - Preview of FATE
snippet.description:
~http://www.wildtangent.com/Games/fate -- Play FATE, the award winning single-player RPG developed by WildTangent. You'll choose your FATE as you travel through the town of Grove with your pet in search of weapons, spells, adventure and fame. Play FATE on the WildTangent Games App today!
